          <comment xml:lang="en">LHV is calculated based on the elemental composition of the substance. Based on the CAS number of the substance (000110-82-7), the chemical formula of the substance is found to be: C6H12, (PubChem 2020). Reference: Kim, S., Chen, J., Cheng, T., Gindulyte, A., He, J., He, S., Li, Q., Shoemaker, B. A., Thiessen, P. A., Yu, B., Zaslavsky, L., Zhang, J., &amp; Bolton, E. E. (2019). PubChem 2019 update: improved access to chemical data. Nucleic acids research, 47(D1), D1102–D1109. https://doi.org/10.1093/nar/gky1033</comment>
